## [function __text\_input\.on\_mouse\_click__\(pos\)](#function-__text_inputon_mouse_click__pos) {#function-__text_inputon_mouse_click__pos}

Is called whenever the user clicks on the widget. Activates the text input for typing text.

__Arguments:__

- `pos` -- An (x, y) coordinates tuple.
	- Type: tuple

